# Configuration Guide:
# APP_ID and API_HASH: Get from https://my.telegram.org
# SESSION: Telethon session string from https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1wjYvtwUo5zDsUvukyafAR9Of-2NYkKsu
# FROM_CHANNEL: Source channel ID(s) separated by spaces (e.g., -1001234567890 -1001234567891)
# TO_CHANNEL: Destination channel ID(s) separated by spaces (e.g., -1001234567892 -1001234567893)
# ADD_FOOTER: Set to True to add custom footer to forwarded messages
# FOOTER_TEXT: Custom text to add at the end of forwarded messages
# BLACKLIST_WORDS: Comma-separated words to filter out (e.g., spam,advertisement)
# WHITELIST_WORDS: Comma-separated words that must be present (optional)
# WEBHOOK_URL: For deployment platforms like Heroku/Render
# PORT: Port for webhook server
# 
# Note: Do not use quotes (") in the values
